{"tid":1824813,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[網路安全] 大家小心 尤其是android機用家 唔好安裝不明來歷既apk檔","createTime":"2020-01-14T17:40:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-15T15:39:44.000Z","uid":88743,"like":29,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"2caf5464c876d10c028858f1b9c5d74db2589af8","tid":1824813,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T17:40:15.000Z","msg":"Hacking a Smartphone by simply sending an SMS?<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/QiM35PmI2dQ?t=180\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FQiM35PmI2dQ%3Ft%3D180&d=RrW1hT%2ByM3GEQeJ1bMSerkPclXdXKQfB%2FlJdEd6ZkMI%3D&h=62fe64a2\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/QiM35PmI2dQ?t=180</a><br />\n<br />\n呢段片就係講個印仔 收左個SMS<br />\nSMS入面有條link, 禁入去會download個apk檔安裝一個應用程式<br />\n裝完之後 雖然睇落個app介面正正常常 但其實你部機已經中左招<br />\n<br />\n後面佢用hacker 既角度可以見到<br />\n個apps係背後連線去hacker部機度.<br />\nhacker可以經呢個連線控制你部機<br />\n可以睇到佢可以download哂你手機上面既SMS檔案, 電話紀錄, 電話簿<br />\n可以用你手機黎send sms<br />\n仲可以瀏覽你手機上面既檔案, 仲可以download佢地<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1824531/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1824531/page/1</a><br />\n格黎開左個PO叫人地裝APK, 起埋佢底見到乜柒都無<br />\n大家睇路"},{"pid":"c9dab1ad5c1a6913740c1d9c64f6d81b4c9d786e","tid":1824813,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T17:43:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9af4900593205f0d3125ed61387794de59d663a9","tid":1824813,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T17:46:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"123efe8e502291babc8eecf51e20c213f1afcf43","tid":1824813,"uid":78033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T17:50:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f2e5698c3ff0f76a9ce107e200fb58bef0c1ccb","tid":18248